       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T6KYC03.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-KYC-DATA.
           05  WS-CUSTOMER-NAME      PIC X(30) VALUE SPACES.
           05  WS-NORMALIZED-NAME    PIC X(30) VALUE SPACES.
           05  WS-UPLOAD-FLAG        PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-CUSTOMER-NAME
           PERFORM 2200-PREPARE-UPLOAD
           DISPLAY WS-UPLOAD-FLAG
           STOP RUN.
       2200-PREPARE-UPLOAD.
           MOVE FUNCTION UPPER-CASE(WS-CUSTOMER-NAME)
              TO WS-NORMALIZED-NAME
           IF WS-NORMALIZED-NAME NOT = SPACES
              MOVE 'Y' TO WS-UPLOAD-FLAG
           END-IF.
